&lt;p id="zh1cMF"&gt;Canoo wrote in a &lt;a href="https://investors.canoo.com/sec-filings/all-sec-filings/content/0001628280-24-037286/0001628280-24-037286.pdf"&gt;quarterly SEC filing&lt;/a&gt; on August 14th that it was “permanently” dropping its headcount as part of a reorganization plan for its Torrance, California facility, and offering to move “approximately 137”...&lt;/p&gt;
